ions of interest and\nprovide all firm and tentative detections along with their morphological and\nspectral characteristics. There are 11 unidentified gamma-ray sources that we\nclassify as firm PWN counterparts, which doubles the PWN population detected by\nthe Fermi-LAT, and 22 gamma-ray sources that are PWN candidates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2022 21:00:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
